Value PROTOCOL (\S+)
Value RECV_Q (\d+)
Value SEND_Q (\d+)
Value LOCAL_ADDRESS (\S+:\d+)
Value FOREIGN_ADDRESS (\S+:\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Proto\s+Recv-Q\s+Send-Q\s+Local Address\s+Foreign Address\s+State\s*$$
